Account management on AetherMUD covers a few key operations:

PASSWORD CHANGE
  Type: password
  Change your login password.  You will be asked for your current password
  first, then to set and confirm a new one.  Passwords must be 5 characters
  or longer.

EMAIL
  Your email address is stored with your account for wizard contact purposes.
  Contact a wizard to update it.

QUITTING PERMANENTLY
  If you wish to delete your character permanently, contact a wizard.  There
  is no self-service character deletion command.  Be certain before asking,
  as deleted characters cannot be recovered.

NOTE
  You are responsible for the security of your account.  Do not share your
  password.  If someone else plays your character and causes trouble, you are
  held responsible.

See also: password
